allorsUnifiedGood.name: AMSS BL450
allorsUnifiedGood.description:
A low cost easily manoeuvrable Towable Belt Loader which is ideal for baggage/cargo loading on all Regional/Commuter Aircraft up to B737/B757 and A320 Series.

Delivers all round high level performance.
Built to last and operate in all weather conditions.
Combines safety of personnel, integrity of the aircraft, secure cargo handling and high build quality without compromise.

brand.name: AMSS
brand.description: AMSS joined JBT AeroTech in 2017 adding new military and commercial products to the JBT family of ground support equipment.  AMSS brings an expanded range of military and commercial cargo loaders, conditioned air units, transporters, belt loaders, towable stairs, staging and other products.  As part of JBT, the AMSS products are supported by AeroTech’s global network of agents, sales professionals, and technical support and parts staff.
